FORMAT: 1A
HOST: https://api.example.com/v1

# Task Management API
A comprehensive API for managing tasks, projects, developers, and notifications.

# Group Developers

## Resource [/developers]

### List all developers [GET]

+ Parameters
    + role (string)
    + team (string)
    + active (boolean)
    + limit (integer)
    + offset (integer)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

### Create a new developer [POST]

+ Request
    + Body (application/json)
            + Attributes (array[DeveloperCreate])

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    Developer created

## Resource [/developers/{developerId}]

### Get developer by ID [GET]

+ Parameters
    + developerId (string) (required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    Developer not found

### Delete a developer [DELETE]

+ Parameters
    + developerId (string) (required)

+ Response 204 (application/json)

    Developer deleted

### Update a developer [PATCH]

+ Parameters
    + developerId (string) (required)

+ Request
    + Body (application/json)
            + Attributes (array[DeveloperUpdate])

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Developer updated

## Resource [/developers/{developerId}/tasks]

### List developer tasks [GET]

+ Parameters
    + developerId (string) (required)
    + status (string)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

