# Group Tasks

## Resource [/tasks]

### List all tasks [GET]

+ Parameters
    + status (string)
    + assignee (string)
    + project (string)
    + priority (string)
    + limit (integer)
    + offset (integer)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

+ Response 401 (application/json)

    Unauthorized

### Create a new task [POST]

+ Request
    + Body (application/json)
            + Attributes (array[TaskCreate])

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    Task created

+ Response 400 (application/json)

    Invalid input

## Resource [/tasks/{taskId}]

### Get task by ID [GET]

+ Parameters
    + taskId (string) (required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    Task not found

### Delete a task [DELETE]

+ Parameters
    + taskId (string) (required)

+ Response 204 (application/json)

    Task deleted

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    Task not found

### Update a task [PATCH]

+ Parameters
    + taskId (string) (required)

+ Request
    + Body (application/json)
            + Attributes (array[TaskUpdate])

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Task updated

+ Response 404 (application/json)

    Task not found

## Resource [/tasks/{taskId}/comments]

### List task comments [GET]

+ Parameters
    + taskId (string) (required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    Successful response

### Add a comment [POST]

+ Parameters
    + taskId (string) (required)

+ Request
    + Body (application/json)
            + Attributes (array[CommentCreate])

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    Comment created

